    "template": "content",
    "texts": [
     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"If you've received a Penalty Charge Notice (PCN), you can either pay it or challenge it if you think it was issued incorrectly.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Pay a PCN\"}",
     "Use this button to pay online now.",
     "{\"template\":\"start-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"end-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eDon't use unofficial payment websites which may mislead you.\u003c/strong\u003e You should always pay for PCNs with us on our secure online system. Read more about \u003ca href=\"/modes/driving/unofficial-selling-websites\"\u003eavoiding payment fraud\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "To pay by phone or by post, or to find out more, go to the \u003ca href=\"/modes/driving/red-routes/penalty-charge-notices/pay-a-pcn\"\u003ePay a Penalty Charge Notice page\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"View the current status of a PCN\"}",
     "You can see more details of the PCN, including its current status.",
     "{\"template\":\"start-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"end-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Challenge a PCN\"}",
     "If you think the PCN has been issued incorrectly you can challenge it by making a representation.",
     "You can make a representation online, in writing, or, in certain circumstances, by phone. It may be possible to give you a quick decision over the phone, depending on the evidence available at the time of calling.",
     " \u003ca href=\"/modes/driving/red-routes/penalty-charge-notices/make-a-representation\"\u003eFind out more about making a representation\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "For more information, telephone us on 0343 222 3333 ( \u003ca href=\"/corporate/terms-and-conditions/tfl-call-charges\"\u003eTfL call charges\u003c/a\u003e ).",
     "Lines are open 08:00-20:00 Monday to Friday."
    ],
